%global packname  IndexNumR
%global packver   0.1.2
%global rlibdir   /usr/local/lib/R/library

Name:             R-CRAN-%{packname}
Version:          0.1.2
Release:          1%{?dist}
Summary:          Index Number Calculation

License:          GPL-2
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-utils 
Requires:         R-utils 

%description
Computes bilateral and multilateral index numbers. It has support for
several standard bilateral indices as well as the GEKS multilateral index
number methods (see Ivancic, Diewert and Fox (2011)
<doi:10.1016/j.jeconom.2010.09.003>) . It also supports updating of GEKS
indexes using several splicing methods.

